                "description": "Sand is an important material that is used in critical stages of construction in concrete, plaster etc. Procuring sand in bulk directly from the source will be cheaper. Your neighbourhood dealer in this case is likely to be costlier, except when you need smaller quantities. When mixing concrete the moisture content must be taken into consideration ",
